Scrips (Matlab & R) for “Habitat preference" section (see also Appendix S4)
Includes Step Selection modeling (SSF) modeling, clogit analysis and Fig 2 plotting
_________________________________________________________________________________

stopDuration_moveDistance_distributions (MATLAB script): 
“stop” duration and “move” distance distributions for SSF modeling. 
table with last point in roost for making a first point for SSF step modeling

SSF_modeling_BC (MATLAB script):
SSF step modeling: random steps for each realized one and creation the table for clogit

SSF_Plotting_BC (R script):
clogit statistical analysis on all the models separately and plotting of Fig 2.

SSF_CreateTables_BC (R script):
clogit statistical analysis and creatiion of tables for Appendix S6
